  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710830/extras/19249bc350981200c5b399a40b9c6aed.poster.avif?t=1737558423\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710830/extras/19249bc350981200c5b399a40b9c6aed.webm?t=1737558423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710830/extras/19249bc350981200c5b399a40b9c6aed.mp4?t=1737558423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Super Nano Blaster</strong> is a shoot-em-up for PC and Mac, offering single-player and local co-op modes, that transports you to a retro-style digital universe. Delve into technology with your vessel and destroy anything that gets in your way!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your mission:</h2><br>Take on the Void, a terrible virus that has slowly infested your world by recycling various entities to fill its ranks.<br>Clear the infected layers and get to the source of the infection.<br>Choose between 8 ships to navigate through epic stages.<br>Master the Switch to avoid obstacles and rack up kills to unlock the Overclock.<br>Dominate the leaderboard and become the top pilot!<br><br>Not enough for you?<br>Set the difficulty to blackhole mode, or even try infinite mode!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710830/extras/690b5b07690652d65457304466b820b9.poster.avif?t=1737558423\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710830/extras/690b5b07690652d65457304466b820b9.webm?t=1737558423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710830/extras/690b5b07690652d65457304466b820b9.mp4?t=1737558423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Single-player or local co-op<br></li><li>8 unique ships to control<br></li><li>Destroy everything in your path<br></li><li>Switch between different planes to avoid enemies<br></li><li>7 levels to explore in 5 difficulty modes<br></li><li>2 game modes: Classic and Infinite</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710830/extras/f11e3091bd74e585cfa6b0299daaa327.poster.avif?t=1737558423\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710830/extras/f11e3091bd74e585cfa6b0299daaa327.webm?t=1737558423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710830/extras/f11e3091bd74e585cfa6b0299daaa327.mp4?t=1737558423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710830/extras/19249bc350981200c5b399a40b9c6aed.poster.avif?t=1737558423\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710830/extras/19249bc350981200c5b399a40b9c6aed.webm?t=1737558423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710830/extras/19249bc350981200c5b399a40b9c6aed.mp4?t=1737558423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Super Nano Blaster</strong> is a shoot-em-up for PC and Mac, offering single-player and local co-op modes, that transports you to a retro-style digital universe. Delve into technology with your vessel and destroy anything that gets in your way!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your mission:</h2><br>Take on the Void, a terrible virus that has slowly infested your world by recycling various entities to fill its ranks.<br>Clear the infected layers and get to the source of the infection.<br>Choose between 8 ships to navigate through epic stages.<br>Master the Switch to avoid obstacles and rack up kills to unlock the Overclock.<br>Dominate the leaderboard and become the top pilot!<br><br>Not enough for you?<br>Set the difficulty to blackhole mode, or even try infinite mode!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710830/extras/690b5b07690652d65457304466b820b9.poster.avif?t=1737558423\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710830/extras/690b5b07690652d65457304466b820b9.webm?t=1737558423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710830/extras/690b5b07690652d65457304466b820b9.mp4?t=1737558423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Single-player or local co-op<br></li><li>8 unique ships to control<br></li><li>Destroy everything in your path<br></li><li>Switch between different planes to avoid enemies<br></li><li>7 levels to explore in 5 difficulty modes<br></li><li>2 game modes: Classic and Infinite</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710830/extras/f11e3091bd74e585cfa6b0299daaa327.poster.avif?t=1737558423\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710830/extras/f11e3091bd74e585cfa6b0299daaa327.webm?t=1737558423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710830/extras/f11e3091bd74e585cfa6b0299daaa327.mp4?t=1737558423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
